        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This macabre staff is crafted from gleaming white bone, a spinal column spiraling out of its base with a skull swinging from the spine's tip. It was handcraft for Nyctessa by her father, a powerful Blood Lord, from her mortal mother's bones.  \nWhen you damage a creature with *Nyctessa\u2019s staff*, that creature gains weakens 2 to negative damage until the end of your next turn.",
